{"tid":1956724,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聽朝十點，你會做乜？","createTime":"2020-04-03T11:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T11:24:19.000Z","uid":228995,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fc01126b4a43b9022025141a550801210734611b","tid":1956724,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:20:18.000Z","msg":"//<br />\n國務院宣布將於明日(4/4)舉行全國性哀悼活動，全國和駐外使領館下半旗，停止公共娛樂活動，為抗擊新型肺炎疫情犧牲烈士和逝世同胞致哀。<br />\n<br />\n公告指明日10時正全國人民默哀3分鐘，汽車、火車、船艦鳴笛，防空警報鳴響致哀，全國停止公共娛樂活動。<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6ea333dd3135dc624e0636a0eacbd1465b9853","tid":1956724,"uid":194525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:20:58.000Z","msg":"開香檳慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"becf8c169ef83d87211d8fdf9877f676f304af79","tid":1956724,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:21:11.000Z","msg":"熱"},{"pid":"88ba67e5e12d8682ffe62bbd738dc0ed5ec5ce3d","tid":1956724,"uid":340221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:22:14.000Z","msg":"鄰國個D哀悼關我撚事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77c7bcfd666237edc4c33d541cfbbf5f7c72bc5","tid":1956724,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:22:30.000Z","msg":"防空警報鳴響致哀<br />\n即係聽朝10點就係偷襲支那好時機<br />\n冇人會覺得真係有防空警報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ceb0f2a6d5fa2cd13be030c6b9e31a75c1292c","tid":1956724,"uid":42090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:24:19.000Z","msg":"一早飲酒好似唔係咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}